@recatm It is inevitable that the functionality of digital painting will be replaced by AI. What is happening now is just a repetition of the history of the functionality of traditional easel painting being replaced by cameras.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: Netizen contribution On January 5, the road sign of Rehe Road in Nanjing was removed, and no new road sign was installed at night. The reason for the removal is currently unknown. In 2015, singer Li Zhi created "Rehe", which has attracted countless young writers to make a pilgrimage since then. The road sign of Rehe Road and the confession wall behind it are even called the Jerusalem of Chinese literary youth.
